s and present first GAMBIT\nresults. GAMBIT can be downloaded from gambit.hepforge.org.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 May 2017 18:00:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Nov 2017 11:26:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-06"}
